                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d682">
                <head>No. 680.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Fish</persName> to General <persName
                            type="to">Sickles</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-12-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 17, 1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your tender of resignation was only hypothetical, and your telegram referred it
                    to alleged publications, unknown here, attributing dissatisfaction which had not
                    been expressed.</p>
                <p>Under these circumstances publication is not deemed necessary, and cannot be
                    authorized.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>FISH.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
